    "We then calculate influence scores for both versions of inputs for each NDA-statement pair in an evaluation sample and NDA-statement in the training data, average them, and select the top three most influential training examples.",
    "For these three influential examples, we additionally incorporate Input×Gradient highlights to streamline the verification process so that participants do not have to review three more NDAs to swiftly verify if the AI's guess is correct.",
    "See Fig. 14 for an example.",
    "All our studies begin with informed consent.",
    "We filter for individuals who have a degree in administration and law, work in legal functions, and are fluent in English."
